{"tid":2192312,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"質疑進廈目的 要求抄低編號  女保安嚇退兩偽警","createTime":"2020-09-07T04:48:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-07T14:00:44.000Z","uid":25558,"like":55,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"8518fb2c31c20891064c848d44e6e3c1369b7776","tid":2192312,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T04:48:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200907/ZCWQQMLDNVGNPCTH3XKG55YVNA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200907%2FZCWQQMLDNVGNPCTH3XKG55YVNA%2F&d=YmBpLFXYotmGfWLbQLkNpzbTr8NPmLdj%2FTsGYWOA6so%3D&h=4d1b8e8b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200907%2FZCWQQMLDNVGNPCTH3XKG55YVNA%2F&h=175fa924\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200907/ZCWQQMLDNVGNPCTH3XKG55YVNA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n質疑進廈目的 要求抄低編號 <br />\n女保安嚇退兩偽警<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】過去一年常有警員執勤時疑違反《警察通例》拒絕展示警員編號或委任證，情況不但令市民無法分辨警察真偽，更可能被賊人利用犯案。日前兩名自稱警員的可疑男子要求進入柴灣一幢大廈查案，但又拒絕被記錄編號，遭女保安拒絕進入後離開。有區議員引述警方指正循冒警方向調查。<br />\n<br />\n記者昨到事發大廈華裕閣，遇上涉事女保安，她指事發上周二晚7時40分，兩名藍衫男子自稱警察進入大廈，她要求對方表明來意及身份，「佢拎個證件出嚟畀我睇，我問佢去幾多樓，搵邊個做咩嘢，佢就話保密，唔方便答，我話要登記資料，佢就即刻轉身走」，整個過程不足一分鐘。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Jg4Qd3jzj0y20QP6ELNlumUbcN4=/1041x1251/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PJVMUXGSNFERVL2J5M4DMXCLPM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FJg4Qd3jzj0y20QP6ELNlumUbcN4%3D%2F1041x1251%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPJVMUXGSNFERVL2J5M4DMXCLPM.jpg&h=b6aa0d1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■大廈閉路電視拍下兩名自稱警員的藍衣男子外貌。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n網民大讚盡忠職守<br />\n<br />\n她指該「委任證」上有相片，但她不懂分辨真偽，「我都唔知佢係真差人定假差人，。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n在社交平台披露事件的東區區議員陳榮泰指，。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n大律師陸偉雄指，大廈保安遇到自稱警員要求進入大廈，可依職責向對方索取委任證或其他證明文件，萬一對方未能提供委任證，應詢問其所駐守警署、職級及部門，以便向警方確認身份；若對方未能提供任何資料，可拒絕其進入。<br />\n<br />\n鑑於便衣警屢拒展示委任證，令市民兵賊難分。陸建議市民遇到便衣警要求搜身或截查，但懷疑其身份，可要求對方出示委任證。。。。。。。。引起途人注意；若被捕可高聲說出個人資料，以保障人身安全及避免受冒警賊人欺騙。<br />\n<br />\n今年8月28日，兩。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/lVHNkInTpBWQJ7UnZAlwnmCQGps=/2100x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WTCYEH627BEWBIOQXTKR3W476A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FlVHNkInTpBWQJ7UnZAlwnmCQGps%3D%2F2100x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWTCYEH627BEWBIOQXTKR3W476A.jpg&h=28645286&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■女保安獲網民大讚盡責。"},{"pid":"1b3ac7261ea325178e252342e637fe783defe2d1","tid":2192312,"uid":334720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T04:51:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"390ac95a5123cf5ebd95210cb4293118e33b82af","tid":2192312,"uid":14494,"like":12,"dislike":3,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T04:52:06.000Z","msg":"女保安涉嫌觸犯國安法"},{"pid":"a7b6441c3d2afc674141d7e3708d980decfa7566","tid":2192312,"uid":76261,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T04:54:15.000Z","msg":"可唔可以請記者問下班狗就哩單野個女保安做得啱唔啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27e74e73d0bb1c695729f02f08484df17ea481be","tid":2192312,"uid":112581,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T04:54:41.000Z","msg":"咁個兩個真係扮得唔似<br />\n下次聽到要抄號碼就打佢一身再咬佢阻差辦公"},{"pid":"fa32f0e97d41efc64db9122be0cb9c0d0621cc3c","tid":2192312,"uid":217641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"27e74e73d0bb1c695729f02f08484df17ea481be","tid":2192312,"uid":112581,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"cited