lass=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b41fb600eaca34f47e4fa4c6c81ee67cf0e5c8d0","tid":2192312,"uid":255162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"27e74e73d0bb1c695729f02f08484df17ea481be","tid":2192312,"uid":112581,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T04:54:41.000Z","msg":"咁個兩個真係扮得唔似<br />\n下次聽到要抄號碼就打佢一身再咬佢阻差辦公"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T05:05:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d02b79c7f042fe111ed6d15f5564ae5e5135800","tid":2192312,"uid":339272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T05:43:13.000Z","msg":"幾多年前？"},{"pid":"67e92b877a36b2a85c369c3a66650e8d5fc43d18","tid":2192312,"uid":73340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T05:46:13.000Z","msg":"揚左既得一單<br />\n成功左既都唔知有幾多單<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f78532748e420abfab0ffb93d71426b80785e545","tid":2192312,"uid":43322,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"27e74e73d0bb1c695729f02f08484df17ea481be","tid":2192312,"uid":112581,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T04:54:41.000Z","msg":"咁個兩個真係扮得唔似<br />\n下次聽到要抄號碼就打佢一身再咬佢阻差辦公"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T05:52:13.000Z","msg":"拎證件出黎係敗筆<br />\n真警一聽到證件2個字已經㩒低佢<br />\n告佢阻差辦公 襲警 煽動公眾情緒"},{"pid":"822a64d3164213dbd0938ae413120625eca680a8","tid":2192312,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f78532748e420abfab0ffb93d71426b80785e545","tid":2192312,"uid":43322,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"27e74e73d0bb1c695729f02f08484df17ea481be","tid":2192312,"uid":112581,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T04:54:41.000Z","msg":"咁個兩個真係扮得唔似<br />\n下次聽到要抄號碼就打佢一身再咬佢阻差辦公"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T05:52:13.000Z","msg":"拎證件出黎係敗筆<br />\n真警一聽到證件2個字已經㩒低佢<br />\n告佢阻差辦公 襲警 煽動公眾情緒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T05:53:00.000Z","msg":"直接送中啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d1e93b7a0abbc3f79e8dc2c85bedee17f56dbe5","tid":2192312,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T05:53:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200825/V3PFRM33TVB7DCGBHFZL2PGT54/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200825%2FV3PFRM33TVB7DCGBHFZL2PGT54%2F&d=YmBpLFXYotmGfWLbQLkNpzbTr8NPmLdj%2FTsGYWOA6so%3D&h=6d68646d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200825%2FV3PFRM33TVB7DCGBHFZL2PGT54%2F&h=44992e67\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200825/V3PFRM33TVB7DCGBHFZL2PGT54/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n兵賊難分 - 高慧然<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/3T60O4theAGeopTNsWdLb5T2OiU=/5760x3840/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FLKGHSEJUBF45NP6FLFEHTKGXU.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F3T60O4theAGeopTNsWdLb5T2OiU%3D%2F5760x3840%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFLKGHSEJUBF45NP6FLFEHTKGXU.JPG&h=52edeead&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n兩個16歲少年在旺角行街，被兩男一女三個自稱警務人員的成年人截停，要求檢查他們的財物，其間三男女盜走兩人各一部約值港幣10000元的手機，在襲擊其中一名少年後迅速逃逸。少年追截不果，去警局報案。案件列作冒充警務人員、盜竊及普通襲擊。<br />\n<br />\n這種奇案，在昔日香港，絕對不可能發生。因為根據《警察通例》第20-14（2）條，便衣人員「不論是否當值，在與巿民接觸和行使警察權力時」，一概必須表明身份及出示委任證。街頭截查巿民，便衣警必須主動出示委任證。若無委任證，巿民當然應該拒絕被查。<br />\n<br />\n但是，兩個少年敢拒絕嗎？不敢。7月24日晚，香港警察在其fb專頁發放一段影片，引用《警察通例》，辯稱警員並非必須在行動期間展示委任證。在這種刻意誤導之下，香港人敢質疑警員身份，敢不配合嗎？<br />\n<br />\n事實是，根據《警察通例》第20-14條第4段，當巿民要求警察出示委任證時，軍裝警員（而非便裝）必須立即出示委任證，除非（a）情況不容許﹔或（b）出示委任證會影響警隊行動及/或危及有關人員安全﹔或（c）要求不合理。所以警察在fb專頁發放的片段，刻意掩飾反送中運動以來警察的違例行為，為他們拒絕出示委任證的荒謬行為狡辯。並且，把亞洲最安全的城巿香港，變成兵賊難分的第三世界。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"b27f764137d74c4ed456d2cc19a04ff0dd5fa40a","tid":2192312,"uid":97080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T05:53:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d2cf93fe275abae1a43b5f4c4404cff84a5b78a","tid":2192312,"uid":308251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T05:57:10.000Z","msg":"阻差辨公<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />解僱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb9b2c1c8f6cf1c5b3465b149557986be0d68411","tid":2192312,"uid":36551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f78532748e420abfab0ffb93d71426b80785e545","tid":2192312,"uid":43322,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"27e74e73d0bb1c695729f02f08484df17ea481be","tid":2192312,"uid":112581,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T04:54:41.000Z","msg":"咁個兩個真係扮得唔似<br />\n下次聽到要抄號碼就打佢一身再咬佢阻差辦公"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T05:52:13.000Z","msg":"拎證件出黎係敗筆<br />\n真警一聽到證件2個字已經㩒低佢<br />\n告佢阻差辦公 襲警 煽動公眾情緒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T06:09:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/waiwai-11_8mmDT_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fwaiwai-11_8mmDT_1200x0.png&h=e65c484c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NWYeTeZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNWYeTeZ.png&h=344478ae&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"449325d67b62c235fa11a84ec0c6a74a656c9bd6","tid":2192312,"uid":89869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"27e74e73d0bb1c695729f02f